74    def exec(self, command: Command) -> RawOutput:
75        args: list[str] = [
76            str(self.client.rac_path),
77            f"{self.host}:{self.port}",
78        ] + command.args
79        if self._debug:
80            print("[DEBUG]", args)
81        try:
82            process = run(
83                args,
84                capture_output=True,
85                text=True,
86                encoding="cp866",
87            )
88            if process.returncode != 0:
89                raise errors.handler(process.stderr)
90            else:
91                if self._debug:
92                    print(process.stdout)
93                return RawOutput(process.stdout)
94        except FileNotFoundError:
95            raise errors.RACNotFoundError
